  to run along the renowned bays of Alcudia and Pollensa.
</p>
<p>
  A qualified triathlon coach will be available to support you with your swimming objectives in the heated pool at the
  <a href="/hotels/zafiro-palace">Zafiro Palace Hotel</a>. Whilst this period will focus on triathlon training, this
