</p>
<p>
  Ciclos Major represents the evolution of an existing provider of cycling trips to the island and the name, whilst
  obviously reflecting cycling, also conjures up the image of the highest peak on the island ‘Puig Major’ which you will
  surely tackle in your time with us.
</p>
<p>
  Our logo design (and that of our cycling jersey) not only represents those lofty peaks, but also your heartbeat as you
  enjoy the finest roads that Mallorca has to offer!!
</p>
<h2>What’s different about Mallorcan Cycling Holidays with Ciclos Major?</h2>
<p>
  We pride ourselves on giving our clients a total experience when they travel with us, and to that end there are
  certain things we don’t do... we don’t just take the easy route and simply deliver our clients to the same old
  ‘honeypots’ that feature in every cycling magazine, and we don’t just follow the same routes, week in, week out!
</p>
<p>
  What we DO strive to do is to give our clients a total experience by constantly sourcing new and interesting routes,
  villages, climbs and café stops in new and exciting areas. We DO make sure our clients get to ride on different and
  exciting roads, using all our guides’ vast knowledge of the island’s roads and routes. We DO strive to make sure our
  clients’ needs and expectations are met, and in terms of cycling we don’t only aim for them to return from their break
  a faster, fitter cyclist, we aim for them to return as a BETTER cyclist! We DO also understand that our clients are
  having a well-earned break from their daily lives, so we also offer a social programme to enable them to not just
  remember the riding when they return home. We have a network of local bars, restaurants and cafés who always offer a
  warm welcome to our clients. For our clients we even slot in a bit of down-time to take in some of the local culture,
  such as live music and cultural events.
</p>
<p>
  We’ll give you a trip to remember, just let us show you how!
</p>
